officialTitle: Substituted Frozen Embryo Transfer Cycles With GnRH-agonist Supplementation
inclusionCriteria:
* Endometrial thickness ≥ 7 mm after stimulation
* 18-45 years
* IVF/ICSI fertilisation
* BMI \> 18,5 \<30 kg/m2
* cycle length 25-34 days
* Must be FEMALE
* Must have minimum age of 18 Years
* Must have maximum age of 45 Years
exclusionCriteria:
* endometrial thickness \< 7 mm or no triple layer endometrium and/or functional follicles
* Uterine abnormality
* Chronic medical disease
* oocyte donation cycles
